#

Porcini Mushroom-Crusted Ribeye with Garlic Herb Butter and Roasted Rainbow Carrots

$35
850 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carbohydrate

Tags:

BeefGourmetDinner

Description

A succulent ribeye steak encrusted with earthy porcini mushrooms, topped with a rich garlic herb butter, served alongside sweet, roasted rainbow carrots for a vibrant and delicious meal.

Ingredients

  • Ribeye steak: 2 (8 oz) pieces
  • Dried porcini mushrooms: 1 cup
  • Unsalted butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • Fresh thyme: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Fresh rosemary: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Rainbow carrots: 1 lb, mixed colors
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
